  "keyFeatures": [
    "Language-neutral binary serialization format with compact, fast encoding",
    "Multi-language runtime support: C++, Java, Python, C#, Go, Ruby, PHP, Rust, Objective-C",
    "Schema-first development with .proto IDL files compiled by protoc",
    "Forward and backward compatibility with schema evolution",
    "Protocol Buffers Editions system for fine-grained feature control",
    "Arena memory allocation for high-performance C++ usage",
    "Well-known types for common data structures (Timestamp, Duration, Struct, etc.)",
    "gRPC integration for RPC service definitions",
    "Plugin architecture for extending protoc code generation",
    "Bazel and CMake build system support"
  ],
